    <teiHeader><fileDesc><titleStmt><title>The Chargé in Colombia (
                        Mokma
                    ) to the Secretary of
                            State</title></titleStmt><sourceDesc><bibl type="frus-volume-id">frus1946v11</bibl><bibl type="frus-document-id">d615</bibl><bibl type="frus-document-number">615</bibl><bibl type="frus-div-subtype">historical-document</bibl></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><settingDesc><setting><date notBefore="1946-06-26T12:00:00-05:00" notAfter="1946-06-26T12:00:00-05:00"/></setting></settingDesc></profileDesc></teiHeader><text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1946-06-26T12:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1946-06-26T12:00:00-05:00" n="615" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d615">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">811.20200(D)/6–2646: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in Colombia</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Mokma</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">us urgent</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Bogotá</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1946-06-26T12:00:00-05:00">June 26, 1946—noon.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received 2:46 p.m.] </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>433. For <gloss target="#t_OIC1">OIC</gloss>. Archbishopric Colombia approached
                    Embassy formally today requesting aid United States broadcast stations relaying
                    special address of Pope to Colombian Catholics July 16 at 11:30 <pb facs="0691" n="673" xml:id="pg_673"/> a.m. Since Vatican broadcast inaudible, Colombia
                    Archbishopric requests Pope’s speech be picked up New York and rebroadcast to
                    Colombia over Emisora de Los Estados Unidos. Ambassador Wiley now Washington
                    will probably support doing everything possible to secure this service because
                    unusual local importance. Please advise if arrangements can be made giving
                    frequencies plans.<note n="65" xml:id="d615fn65">In telegram 367, July 1, 1946,
                        to Bogotá, the Department indicated that it was impossible to give the aid
                        requested for budgetary reasons (811.20200(D)/6-2646).</note>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Mokma</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
